name: UIPrintInfo.Duplex
desc: Constants that describe the duplex mode of a selected printer.

items.name: case none
items.desc: No double-sided (duplex) printing; single-sided printing only.

items.name: case longEdge
items.desc: Duplex printing that flips the back page along the long edge of the paper.

items.name: case shortEdge
items.desc: Duplex print that flips the back page along the short edge of the paper.
